    # Chi "See these pointy bits? They have different purposes."
    Chi "¿Ves estas puntas? Tienen propósitos diferentes."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2832
translate spanish d17a569_4d798324:

    # Chi "The two pointy ones are showing the seconds and minutes, whereas the wider two are showing hours and days."
    Chi "Las dos finas marcan los segundos y los minutos, mientras que las dos más anchas muestran las horas y los días."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2835
translate spanish d17a569_72743cd7:

    # Z "I... don't understand. What happened to your cousin... she appeared to fully expect something to happen to her and she just... died?"
    Z "Yo... no entiendo. ¿Qué pasó con tu prima... parecía esperar completamente que algo le sucediera y simplemente... ¿murió?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2836
translate spanish d17a569_62e1d61a:

    # Chi "My people, my kind, we all have a knowledge. Everything that lives owes a death, and we know when ours is to come."
    Chi "Mi gente, mi clase, todos tenemos un conocimiento. Todo lo que vive debe una muerte, y sabemos cuándo llegará la nuestra."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2837
translate spanish d17a569_4a80e528:

    # Chi "Our tribe was founded on this, in fact. Each of us are aware of the length of time we have to live."
    Chi "Nuestra tribu se fundó en esto, de hecho. Cada uno de nosotros es consciente del tiempo que tenemos para vivir."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2840
translate spanish d17a569_b2dc59ab:

    # Chi "With this knowledge bestowed upon us, we created the time-piece and carried it through our journey, never to forget."
    Chi "Con este conocimiento que se nos otorgó, creamos el cronómetro y lo llevamos en nuestro viaje, para no olvidar nunca."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2844
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_4df7ed4f:

    # Z "Why do you keep track of this time? I don't know when I will die, and I think I would never want to know in advance."
    Z "¿Por qué llevas la cuenta del tiempo? Yo no sé cuándo moriré, y creo que nunca querría saberlo de antemano."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2845
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_14ccd5a0:

    # Chi "Well... your death is not predetermined, is it? You can die in a fight, or in an accident, and if you don't you might get lucky and grow old."
    Chi "Bueno... tu muerte no está predeterminada, ¿verdad? Puedes morir en una pelea, o en un accidente, y si no, podrías tener suerte y envejecer."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2846
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_bde8512f:

    # Chi "This goes for us too, except that we don't really grow old at all. Some of us may live for thirty, some of us for fifty years."
    Chi "Esto también aplica para nosotros, excepto que realmente no envejecemos. Algunos de nosotros pueden vivir treinta años, algunos cincuenta."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2847
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_1e773c5a:

    # Chi "And, barring incidents or murder, we know in advance when each of us will pass."
    Chi "Y, salvo incidentes o asesinatos, sabemos de antemano cuándo cada uno de nosotros morirá."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2848
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_81b0008b:

    # Chi "This knowledge is certain, inescapable and absolute."
    Chi "Este conocimiento es certero, ineludible y absoluto."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2849
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_2dbd0837:

    # Chi "To remind us of this limit we carry within ourselves, our forefathers decided to create this time-piece."
    Chi "Para recordarnos este límite que llevamos dentro, nuestros antepasados decidieron crear este reloj de arena."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2850
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_aa79057a:

    # Z "So the time-piece serves as a reminder how much time you have left?"
    Z "Así que el reloj sirve como un recordatorio de cuánto tiempo te queda."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2851
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_69cb0aa7:

    # Chi "Yes... but, as I said, it's a practical thing, not a philosophical abstraction. Our knowledge is certain. We write down the time, and with this device, we can pin point it to hours, minutes and even seconds."
    Chi "Sí... pero, como dije, es algo práctico, no una abstracción filosófica. Nuestro conocimiento es certero. Escribimos el tiempo, y con este dispositivo podemos precisarlo a horas, minutos e incluso segundos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2852
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_d800fcd9:

    # Chi "And when the time has come, we gather together... and send the person on their eternal journey. When it is common knowledge and you are about to face the end, it is better not to be alone."
    Chi "Y cuando llega el momento, nos reunimos... y enviamos a la persona en su viaje eterno. Cuando es conocimiento común y estás a punto de enfrentarte al final, es mejor no estar solo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2859
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_19be0114:

    # Z "You mentioned a journey. What's that about?"
    Z "Mencionaste un viaje. ¿De qué trata eso?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2862
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_b343440b:

    # Chi "We call our tribe the Sapa... I'm... sure it had a different pronounciation, back in the lands where it all started."
    Chi "Llamamos a nuestra tribu los Sapa... Estoy... segura de que tenía otra pronunciación en las tierras donde todo empezó."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2863
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_d5829f35:

    # Chi "Anyway... Sapa is the concept of our journey. The journey for time."
    Chi "De todos modos... Sapa es el concepto de nuestro viaje. El viaje por el tiempo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2864
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_39d6eb40:

    # Chi "When our people first discovered that their unique condition was measurable, and that our death was predetermined, we banded together."
    Chi "Cuando nuestra gente descubrió por primera vez que su condición única era medible, y que nuestra muerte estaba predeterminada, nos unimos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2865
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_5a6bf082:

    # Chi "Over the decades and centuries, we travelled the lands looking for answers, a solution, an escape from the wheel of time... eventually, the journey stopped in this place."
    Chi "A lo largo de las décadas y los siglos, hemos viajado por las tierras buscando respuestas, una solución, una escapatoria del ciclo del tiempo... eventualmente, el viaje terminó en este lugar."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2866
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_889e724c:

    # Chi "Maybe one day we will move again. Until then... we learned to make the most of the time we have."
    Chi "Tal vez algún día nos mudemos de nuevo. Hasta entonces... hemos aprendido a aprovechar el tiempo que tenemos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2867
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_96330a60:

    # Z "And were you...?"
    Z "¿Y tú estabas...?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2868
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_a033f2eb:

    # Chi "Finding answers? No... not yet. And we probably won't be in my lifetime."
    Chi "¿Encontrando respuestas? No... todavía no. Y probablemente no será en mi vida."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2869
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_8dadaee8:

    # Chi "But to remind us of our journey, we have the time-piece. You see why it would be important to us?"
    Chi "Pero para recordarnos nuestro viaje, tenemos el reloj de arena. ¿Ves por qué sería importante para nosotros?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2876
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_cfaf367e:

    # Z "What's the short pointer on the bottom right for?"
    Z "¿Cuál es el marcador corto en la parte inferior derecha?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2879
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_f90af05d:

    # Chi "Oh, that split one?"
    Chi "¿Oh, ese que estaba roto?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2880
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_da67bc52:

    # Chi "That's the one counting the years!"
    Chi "Ese es el que cuenta los años."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2881
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_9e82fd26:

    # Z "Why does it look like an axe?"
    Z "¿Por qué parece un hacha?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2882
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_11eea09c:

    # Chi "That one was not always like this..."
    Chi "Ese no siempre fue así..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2883
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_f9aa1826:

    # Chi "I was told that the reason why it is pointing sideways is that no matter how many years you were given at birth, we are all supposed to be equal."
    Chi "Me dijeron que la razón por la que apunta de lado es que, no importa cuántos años te hayan dado al nacer, se supone que todos debemos ser iguales."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2884
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_0812111b:

    # Chi "Some of us live longer, and some don't. That's life!"
    Chi "Algunos de nosotros vivimos más tiempo, y otros no. ¡Así es la vida!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2890
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_46d9d5a6:

    # Z "How does it work, your condition, I mean?"
    Z "¿Cómo funciona, tu condición, digo?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2891
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_e4472fa7:

    # Z "Is it a disease? Do you always inherit it?"
    Z "¿Es una enfermedad? ¿Siempre se hereda?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2892
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_eca67b67:

    # Chi "You should ask my sister about this! Something about a... dominant disorder?"
    Chi "Deberías preguntarle a mi hermana sobre esto. ¿Algo sobre un... trastorno dominante?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2893
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_00be465f:

    # Chi "No matter what we do, with whom we couple, or under what circumstances... everyone in our bloodline is born with a unique heartbeat pattern."
    Chi "No importa lo que hagamos, con quién nos emparejemos o bajo qué circunstancias... todos en nuestra línea de sangre nacen con un patrón único de latidos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2894
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_45b40ce6:

    # Chi "Count thirty heartbeats without a pause, and that's your lifespan! Everyone of us has their own number."
    Chi "Cuenta treinta latidos sin pausa, y esa es tu esperanza de vida. Cada uno de nosotros tiene su propio número."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2895
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_a87f9890:

    # Z "This... sounds like an unbelievable curse."
    Z "Esto... suena como una maldición increíble."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2896
translate spanish d17a_time_piece_questions_dd56d736:

    # Chi "Cars are unbelievable for some! Everything is unbelievable, until you see the patterns, the gears!"
    Chi "¡Los coches son increíbles para algunos! ¡Todo es increíble, hasta que ves los patrones, los engranajes!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2902
translate spanish d17a579_7a77d033:

    # Fa "Hold on a minute... Chili, if everyone of you has a number, then you two have one as well?"
    Fa "Espera un momento... Chili, si cada uno de vosotros tiene un número, ¿entonces vosotras dos también tenéis uno?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2903
translate spanish d17a579_0a0d37c3:

    # Fa "Why didn't you say anything?"
    Fa "¿Por qué no dijiste nada?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2906
translate spanish d17a579_2a374eee:

    # Chi "Sorry... we don't tell outsiders. My sister insisted."
    Chi "Lo siento... No se lo decimos a los forasteros. Mi hermana insistió."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2909
translate spanish d17a579_b165a705:

    # Chi "And yes, sure we do. I have one, so does she. Mine's lower though."
    Chi "Y sí, claro que tenemos. Yo tengo uno y ella también. Aunque el mío es más bajo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2910
translate spanish d17a579_b0578858:

    # Chi "Why?"
    Chi "¿Por qué?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2913
translate spanish d17a579_09e99d85:

    # Fa "What do you mean by lower..."
    Fa "¿Qué quieres decir con más bajo...?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2916
translate spanish d17a579_32e4c90a:

    # Fa "Chili... what is your number then?"
    Fa "Chili... ¿cuál es tu número entonces?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2921
translate spanish d17a579_3b276069:

    # Chi "Mine? Oh! That's two, and..."
    Chi "¿El mío? ¡Oh! Son dos, y..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2924
translate spanish d17a579_bed89b4e:

    # Chi "...Five!"
    Chi "... ¡Cinco!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2927
translate spanish d17a579_07db8355:

    # Fa "...!"
    Fa "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2928
translate spanish d17a579_b6654695:

    # Fa "Twenty five..."
    Fa "Veinticinco..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2931
translate spanish d17a579_ff0915fe:

    # Fa "You only have twenty five years?"
    Fa "¿Sólo te quedan veinticinco años?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2934
translate spanish d17a579_686de92d:

    # Fa "I..."
    Fa "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2935
translate spanish d17a579_4a59f47a:

    # Chi "Fangs...? What's wrong?"
    Chi "¿Fangs...? ¿Qué pasa?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2938
translate spanish d17a579_9e941efe:

    # Pe "I'm sorry, Fangs..."
    Pe "Lo siento, Fangs..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2941
translate spanish d17a579_e32c073a:

    # Fa "{i}*gasp*{/i}"
    Fa "{i}*jadeo*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2942
translate spanish d17a579_42d65ce9:

    # Pe "There were... multiple reasons for not telling you about this."
    Pe "Había... múltiples razones para no decirte esto."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2943
translate spanish d17a579_b4bca040:

    # Pe "I didn't want you to think I only wanted the laboratory to look for a solution for all this..."
    Pe "No quería que pensaras que sólo quería el laboratorio para buscar una solución para todo esto..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2944
translate spanish d17a579_3609ae68:

    # Pe "...and I did not want you to treat her differently."
    Pe "... y no quería que la trataras de manera diferente."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2947
translate spanish d17a579_ec3668f4:

    # Fa "I don't blame you, Pepper. You told me not to ask."
    Fa "No te culpo, Pepper. Dijiste que no preguntara."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2948
translate spanish d17a579_c4ca80ee:

    # Fa "But... I still should have, and that's on me."
    Fa "Pero... aún debería haberlo hecho, y eso es culpa mía."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2951
translate spanish d17a579_5ace63fb:

    # Chi "Fangs...!"
    Chi "¡Fangs...!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2954
translate spanish d17a579_e7e43ee0:

    # Chi "You don't need to be sad for me. That's how life is. I have always known this, remember?"
    Chi "No te preocupes por mí. Así es la vida. Siempre lo he sabido, ¿lo recuerdas?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2955
translate spanish d17a579_37ddcc52:

    # Chi "We learn to make our peace with it."
    Chi "Aprendemos a hacer las paces con ello."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2958
translate spanish d17a579_b56b9d6f:

    # Fa "I... I'm sorry, Chili. I need time to process this."
    Fa "Yo... lo siento, Chili. Necesito tiempo para procesar esto."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2961
translate spanish d17a579_05f84ef8:

    # Fa "[persistent.player_name]... do you mind if we take a breather?"
    Fa "[persistent.player_name]... ¿te importa si tomamos un descanso?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2964
translate spanish d17a579_781d56fe:

    # Fa "We... will have a gathering in two hours. We will decide what happens next with the settlement."
    Fa "Nosotros... tendremos una reunión en dos horas. Decidiremos qué pasa después con el asentamiento."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2967
translate spanish d17a579_87b498cc:

    # Fa "I want everyone to give their vote, this time. Will I see you there?"
    Fa "Quiero que todos den su voto esta vez. ¿Te veré allí?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2970
translate spanish d17a579_35acc7d9:

    # Z "You will. Let us take a rest, and then decide. See you later."
    Z "Lo harás. Descansemos un poco y luego decidimos. Nos vemos más tarde."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2978
translate spanish d17a579_12d4310e:

    # Zt "I might use the time to learn more about this place, before I cast my vote..."
    Zt "Podría usar el tiempo para aprender más sobre este lugar antes de emitir mi voto..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2988
translate spanish d17a_aftermath_overview_1f666415:

    # Z "It looks desolate, but still..."
    Z "Se ve desolado, pero aún así..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2994
translate spanish d17a_aftermath_overview_2354e061:

    # "You enter a room that vastly differs from the rest of the basement."
    "Entras en una habitación que es muy diferente al resto del sótano."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2995
translate spanish d17a_aftermath_overview_4f98568c:

    # "Purple light, plants and generator noises surround you. It's like you are back in the bunker, once more."
    "Luz púrpura, plantas y ruidos de generador te rodean. Es como si estuvieras de vuelta en el búnker, una vez más."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2998
translate spanish d17a_aftermath_overview_42145ee3:

    # Stw "Hey there, my name is Ira. Thank you for liberating us last night. We have been under their occupation for many months now."
    Stw "Ey, me llamo Ira. Gracias por liberarnos anoche. Hemos estado bajo su ocupación durante muchos meses."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:2999
translate spanish d17a_aftermath_overview_b9f92fcb:

    # Ira "Can I do something for you?"
    Ira "¿Puedo hacer algo por ti?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3002
translate spanish d17a_aftermath_overview_ccbd876f:

    # Z "I came to learn more about the way you live."
    Z "Vine a aprender más sobre vuestra forma de vida."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3005
translate spanish d17a_aftermath_overview_303e6293:

    # Ira "Sure, anything specific? Ask away."
    Ira "Claro, ¿algo en específico? Pregunta."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3015
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_6cb5ffd5:

    # Z "Do you grow your food in here?"
    Z "¿Cultiváis aquí vuestra comida?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3018
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_04fdb8ab:

    # Ira "Yes, we do indeed. This facility has several purposes."
    Ira "Sí, lo hacemos. Este lugar tiene varios propósitos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3021
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_986a2a9a:

    # Ira "Mainly, we have worked out how to grow fast yielding crops of a number of vegetables."
    Ira "Principalmente, hemos trabajado para cultivar vegetales de rápido rendimiento."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3022
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_916dded1:

    # Ira "We are experimenting special strands that we hope will be resistant to the desert climate and still grow."
    Ira "Estamos experimentando con variedades especiales que esperamos sean resistentes al clima del desierto y aun así crezcan."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3023
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_1e00e8f4:

    # Ira "It's slow going, but we are getting some results."
    Ira "Es un progreso lento, pero estamos obteniendo algunos resultados."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3024
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_eb5f10dc:

    # Ira "You must have seen some of them already."
    Ira "Debes haber visto a algunos de ellos ya."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3025
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_e6202ec6:

    # Z "Have you built this place yourself?"
    Z "¿Has construido este lugar tú misma?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3026
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_6b5f1b8b:

    # Ira "Oh.. no, not exactly."
    Ira "¡Oh... no, no exactamente!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3029
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_b7830045:

    # Ira "Our forefathers have roamed the lands and collected invaluable components. We simply... try to maintain what they did."
    Ira "Nuestros antepasados han vagado por las tierras recolectando componentes invaluables. Nosotros simplemente... intentamos mantener lo que hicieron."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3030
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_858a4a2f:

    # Z "It is certainly impressive... some of those materials are in pretty good condition and seem to resist decay."
    Z "Es ciertamente impresionante... algunos de estos materiales están en muy buenas condiciones y parecen resistir la descomposición."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3031
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_7ffc5365:

    # Ira "It's a particular source of frustration for myself, that one. I don't quite know what happened, a few generations ago, but we have lost the ability to find, or create those materials."
    Ira "Esa en particular es una fuente de frustración para mí. No sé muy bien qué ocurrió hace unas generaciones, pero hemos perdido la capacidad de encontrar o crear esos materiales."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3032
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_51b525f1:

    # Ira "We've learned our lesson though. We are now recording everything in multiple different ways, and committing much to memory."
    Ira "Hemos aprendido nuestra lección, eso sí. Ahora estamos grabando todo de múltiples maneras diferentes y memorizando mucho."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3033
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_73866fa6:

    # Z "How come the people who managed to capture you did not destroy this place?"
    Z "¿Cómo es que las personas que lograron capturaros no destruyeron este lugar?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3034
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_30be8046:

    # Ira "Food is somewhat scarce in the wasteland. They were a little mad, but not suicidal. Why throw away a reliable source of food?"
    Ira "La comida es algo escasa en el páramo. Estaban un poco locos, pero no suicidas. ¿Por qué desperdiciar una fuente confiable de comida?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3041
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_615c0f17:

    # Z "How did your people survive over the years?"
    Z "¿Cómo sobrevivió tu gente a lo largo de los años?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3044
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_ce4b5c58:

    # "She smiles, slightly..."
    "Sonríe, levemente..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3047
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_c6b9c1ae:

    # Ira "Many of us may not live long lives, but they still live a life, and they fall in love..."
    Ira "Muchos de nosotros quizás no vivamos vidas largas, pero aún así viven una vida, y se enamoran..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3048
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_bdbe3f2d:

    # Ira "We are open to outsiders, even if we keep our condition a secret."
    Ira "Estamos abiertos a forasteros, incluso si mantenemos en secreto nuestra condición."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3051
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_3b8317a0:

    # Ira "Mind you, that is before long lasting consequences happen. Those who merged with our tribe and became family knew that their children would carry the condition. And yet..."
    Ira "Ten en cuenta que eso es antes de que ocurran consecuencias duraderas. Aquellos que se fusionaron con nuestra tribu y se convirtieron en familia sabían que sus hijos llevarían la condición. Y, sin embargo..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3054
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_897e4017:

    # Ira "Life always finds a way, as they say."
    Ira "La vida siempre encuentra un camino, como dicen."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3062
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_299c4227:

    # Z "How come no one joined Pepper?"
    Z "¿Cómo es que nadie se unió a Pepper?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3065
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_73a270f4:

    # Ira "Pardon me? Pepper...? I don't..."
    Ira "¿Perdón? ¿Pepper...? Yo no..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3068
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_b6aafb61:

    # Ira "Oh, right. You are talking about Elvira."
    Ira "Oh, claro. Estás hablando de Elvira."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3071
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_289b10c5:

    # Z "How come no one joined Elvira into the bunker?"
    Z "¿Cómo es que nadie se unió a Elvira en el búnker?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3074
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_f51c0b99:

    # Ira "Elvira left because she wanted to properly research the source of the tribe's condition."
    Ira "Elvira se fue porque quería investigar adecuadamente la fuente de la condición de la tribu."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3075
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_fb1488e0:

    # Ira "While I am grateful for her commitment, Mina was the only one following her on this path. Perhaps because she always somehow looked up to her sister."
    Ira "Aunque estoy agradecida por su compromiso, Mina fue la única que la siguió en este camino. Tal vez porque siempre admiró a su hermana de alguna manera."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3078
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_0bf30455:

    # Z "And why is that?"
    Z "¿Y eso por qué?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3081
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_25c17059:

    # Ira "While Elvira's decision to leave us for your bunker to research a way to prolong Mina's short life expectancy is noble..."
    Ira "Aunque la decisión de Elvira de dejarnos por tu búnker para investigar una forma de prolongar la corta esperanza de vida de Mina es noble..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3082
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_93aa3308:

    # Ira "...we wondered, what does this mean for our journey? Our culture?"
    Ira "... nos preguntamos, ¿qué significa esto para nuestro viaje? ¿Nuestra cultura?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3085
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_135817cc:

    # Z "You feared that it would change your people?"
    Z "¿Temías que eso cambiara a tu gente?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3088
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_04f5c34b:

    # Ira "I suppose. The Sapa teaches us patience, connection, and acceptance in regards to our condition, and life as a whole..."
    Ira "Supongo. El Sapa nos enseña paciencia, conexión y aceptación con respecto a nuestra condición y a la vida en general..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3089
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_760289d2:

    # Ira "Many of us hold the firm belief that our lives, however long they might be, should be enjoyed and celebrated within our community."
    Ira "Muchos de nosotros tenemos la firme creencia de que nuestras vidas, por largas o cortas que sean, deben disfrutarse y celebrarse dentro de nuestra comunidad."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3092
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_2cdac19c:

    # Ira "From what I have seen today, I presume you can see that our values are fundamentally different from what the bunker and their people stand for."
    Ira "Por lo que he visto hoy, supongo que puedes ver que nuestros valores son fundamentalmente diferentes de lo que el búnker y su gente representan."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3095
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_62780b37:

    # Z "So, what happens now? Where would your path lead next, if it was up to you?"
    Z "¿Y ahora qué? ¿Dónde llevaría tu camino después, si dependiera de ti?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3098
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_d9dcc39e:

    # Ira "There is no denying that thanks to your people, we have been given a new chance to continue our journey, or at least prepare for it."
    Ira "No se puede negar que, gracias a tu gente, se nos ha dado una nueva oportunidad para continuar nuestro viaje, o al menos prepararnos para ello."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3099
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_38d71a30:

    # Ira "Planning the next step, however, will take some time. We should also not lose sight of what we already have."
    Ira "Planear el próximo paso, sin embargo, tomará algo de tiempo. Tampoco debemos perder de vista lo que ya tenemos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3102
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_3c023cb8:

    # Ira "Before we were attacked, we had made this place our home, and it used to be functional, nice and... well..."
    Ira "Antes de que nos atacaran, habíamos hecho de este lugar nuestro hogar, y solía ser funcional, agradable y... bueno..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3103
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_f411ac97:

    # Ira "...a real home."
    Ira "... ¡un verdadero hogar!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3106
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_43efc4d5:

    # Ira "If we decide to rebuild, then I have ideas for how to make it more habitable again."
    Ira "Si decidimos reconstruir, entonces tengo ideas sobre cómo hacerlo más habitable nuevamente."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3109
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_81417920:

    # Ira "But in truth, it is our custom to not linger too many years in the same place. It might be time to depart again."
    Ira "Pero en verdad, es nuestra costumbre no quedarnos demasiados años en el mismo lugar. Quizá sea hora de partir de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3112
translate spanish d17a_hothouse_questions_b921dd1d:

    # Z "Thank you for sharing your thoughts."
    Z "Gracias por compartir tus pensamientos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3119
translate spanish d17a611_f26a939b:

    # Z "Alright. I think I will move on now."
    Z "De acuerdo. Creo que ahora seguiré adelante."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3122
translate spanish d17a611_449e8585:

    # Ira "Thank you again. You are always welcome to visit, and always will have our gratitude for what you did today."
    Ira "Gracias de nuevo. Siempre serás bienvenido a visitarnos, y siempre tendrás nuestra gratitud por lo que hiciste hoy."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3133
translate spanish d17a611_5b9fad7f:

    # "You walk through the concrete rubble, and approach a settler..."
    "Caminas entre los escombros de concreto y te acercas a un colono..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3136
translate spanish d17a611_85495335:

    # Stm "Good morning... Ah, it's been a while since I could honestly say this."
    Stm "Buenos días... Ah, hace tiempo que no podía decir esto sinceramente."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3139
translate spanish d17a611_5503b4b3:

    # Z "Good morning, indeed."
    Z "Buenos días, de verdad."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3147
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_5dae020c:

    # Z "I have a general question..."
    Z "Tengo una pregunta general..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3148
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_a2aabd8f:

    # Z "Looking at this place and how it is structured... how did you manage to survive for all these years?"
    Z "Mirando este lugar y cómo está estructurado... ¿Cómo lograron sobrevivir todos estos años?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3149
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_0af91a83:

    # Z "Savages roam these lands quite frequently."
    Z "Los salvajes vagan por estas tierras con bastante frecuencia."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3152
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_8bf980c0:

    # Stm "We tend to not attract much attention usually. Few people are interested in what appear to be long abandoned ruins, thankfully."
    Stm "Tendemos a no llamar mucho la atención usualmente. Pocas personas están interesadas en lo que parecen ser ruinas abandonadas desde hace mucho, afortunadamente."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3153
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_ec0e86a1:

    # Stm "But... every now and then some will come closer."
    Stm "Pero... de vez en cuando, algunos se acercan más."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3156
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_357fa1c3:

    # Stm "And not always with good intentions."
    Stm "Y no siempre con buenas intenciones."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3159
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_c080a8af:

    # Stm "But... I suppose this is a danger we chose to live with, it is part of our journey."
    Stm "Pero... supongo que este es un peligro que elegimos vivir, forma parte de nuestro viaje."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3162
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_34c00f56:

    # Z "Your journey?"
    Z "¿Tu viaje?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3165
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_2e2bdb8f:

    # Stm "Once, maybe twice a lifetime, we move to a new place in the world, scavenge the area, in our perennial search for the world's secrets..."
    Stm "Una vez, tal vez dos en una vida, nos mudamos a un nuevo lugar en el mundo, exploramos el área, en nuestra búsqueda perenne de los secretos del mundo..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3166
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_859b2c05:

    # Stm "...my father, his father, and his grand father have been doing the same."
    Stm "... mi padre, su padre y su abuelo han estado haciendo lo mismo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3169
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_5138df4b:

    # Stm "The Sapa is a generational task... one I cannot expect to see the end during my lifetime."
    Stm "El Sapa es una tarea generacional... algo que no espero ver terminado durante mi vida."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3172
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_812b7511:

    # "He holds in for a moment..."
    "Él aguanta un momento..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3175
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_8d99cb68:

    # Stm "Purpose is a powerful driving force, you know. And purpose is what keeps us together."
    Stm "El propósito es una fuerza motriz poderosa, ¿sabes? Y el propósito es lo que nos mantiene unidos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3176
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_d747cbbc:

    # Stm "We all share the same fate after all..."
    Stm "Todos compartimos el mismo destino al final..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3177
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_bd47ee74:

    # Stm "But... some of us have been growing ever more demotivated....or frustrated even."
    Stm "Pero... algunos de nosotros hemos estado cada vez más desmotivados... o incluso frustrados."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3180
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_0773bce9:

    # Stm "And I cannot blame them really, even if we don't necessarily share the same sentiments."
    Stm "Y no puedo culparlos realmente, aunque no necesariamente compartamos los mismos sentimientos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3183
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_c5130e69:

    # Z "How so?"
    Z "¿Cómo es eso?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3186
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_ea5fe809:

    # Stm "It's just that..."
    Stm "Es solo eso..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3189
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_ffc9124a:

    # Stm "...everybody will eventually die, and every person knows this. But in a nebulous, abstract way."
    Stm "... todos eventualmente morirán, y cada persona lo sabe. Pero de una manera nebulosa y abstracta."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3190
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_a2dd89cf:

    # Stm "But us? We know {i}when{/i}, and that...is different. It makes death tangible, real."
    Stm "Pero nosotros... sabemos {i}cuándo{/i}, y eso... es diferente. Hace que la muerte sea tangible, real."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3193
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_b2aad50c:

    # Stm "What would you do if you knew? If you had absolute certainty, down to the day? How would you choose to spend your time?"
    Stm "¿Qué harías si lo supieras? Si tuvieras la certeza absoluta, hasta el día exacto. ¿Cómo elegirías pasar tu tiempo?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3194
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_fd86ad09:

    # Stm "Would you try and make the most of it? For you? For others?"
    Stm "¿Intentarías aprovecharlo al máximo? ¿Por ti? ¿Por otros?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3195
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_618d0a19:

    # Stm "How many breaths would you spend on things you think do not matter?"
    Stm "¿Cuántos alientos gastarías en cosas que piensas que no importan?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3196
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_4b671dd0:

    # Stm "So yes, I understand them. As I understood Elvira."
    Stm "Sí, los entiendo. Como entendí a Elvira."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3199
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_1fdd103c:

    # Z "I guess you don't see eye to eye?"
    Z "Supongo que no estáis de acuerdo, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3200
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_248809a2:

    # Stm "No, it's not that. At least I don't think so..."
    Stm "No, no es eso. O al menos no lo creo..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3201
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_8083f77f:

    # Stm "She kept telling us how our ways are ineffective, how we are squandering our days chasing fairytales."
    Stm "Seguía diciendo cómo nuestros métodos son ineficaces, cómo estamos desperdiciando nuestros días persiguiendo cuentos de hadas."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3202
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_35674504:

    # Stm "And then... one day, she came upon your people and suggested joining you, with a promise of real access to the technology we had until then only learned from in abstraction, from old books."
    Stm "Y entonces... un día, se acercó a nuestra gente y sugirió unirse a vosotros, con la promesa de un acceso real a la tecnología que hasta entonces solo habíamos aprendido en abstracción, de libros antiguos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3203
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_a0019583:

    # Stm "An actual way to try and {i}fight this{/i}, in her words..."
    Stm "Una forma real de intentar {i}luchar contra esto{/i}, según sus palabras..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3206
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_44dfd980:

    # Stm "...and we declined."
    Stm "... y nos negamos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3212
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_2b570b29:

    # Stm "{i}*sigh*{/i}.. I saw your leader, when they came to petition us. She is strongly driven to fight, to build her own future."
    Stm "{i}*suspiro*{/i}.. Vi a tu líder cuando vino a pedirnos ayuda. Está fuertemente motivada a luchar, a construir su propio futuro."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3215
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_e58711e9:

    # Stm "...I wonder if our forefathers were also this determined, when they started their journey?"
    Stm "... ¡me pregunto si nuestros antepasados eran igual de determinados cuando comenzaron su viaje!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3218
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_544d135b:

    # Stm "I also wonder about our path forward sometimes."
    Stm "A veces me pregunto hacia dónde vamos..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3219
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_7a63235d:

    # Stm "And this now? It got me thinking..."
    Stm "¿Y esto ahora? Me dejó pensando..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3220
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_44dececa:

    # Stm "Do we continue our journey, or will we forfeit our ways and start a different approach?"
    Stm "¿Continuamos nuestro viaje o abandonamos nuestro camino y empezamos un enfoque diferente?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3223
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_2be414b7:

    # Z "Do you think your people want change?"
    Z "¿Crees que tu gente quiere cambiar?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3226
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_616ba423:

    # Stm "I believe that people are uncertain, and divided in their opinions about the future."
    Stm "Creo que la gente está incierta y dividida en sus opiniones sobre el futuro."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3229
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_2e1d0742:

    # Stm "However we decide though, we will stay one family. Of that I am certain."
    Stm "Sin embargo, decidan lo que decidan, seguiremos siendo una familia. De eso estoy seguro."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3230
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_4e592eb1:

    # Stm "Because... after all... we all share the same fate, at the end of our lives."
    Stm "Porque... al final... todos compartimos el mismo destino, al final de nuestras vidas."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3233
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_73bf05d2:

    # Z "May you find your peace in whatever direction your people take."
    Z "Que encuentres la paz en la dirección que tome tu gente."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3240
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_d7c1bf80:

    # Z "The time piece was stopped... how does this affect you?"
    Z "La pieza del tiempo se detuvo... ¿cómo os afecta esto?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3243
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_8a840fee:

    # Stm "It did... during the last months, some of us died... and we could not even come together."
    Stm "Sí... durante los últimos meses, algunos de nosotros murieron... y ni siquiera pudimos reunirnos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3246
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_a3eb9314:

    # Stm "Poor Dinara. Bless her soul..."
    Stm "Pobre Dinara. Bendita sea su alma..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3252
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_8b9df982:

    # Stm "It scares me, sometimes. Before, I knew the exact second I would eventually pass."
    Stm "A veces me asusta. Antes, sabía el segundo exacto en que eventualmente moriría."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3255
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_questions_b9c3337f:

    # Stm "Now... if anything, I will know the rough time of the day."
    Stm "Ahora... si acaso, sabré la hora aproximada del día."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3262
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_18ad3f1a:

    # Z "It was insightful speaking with you. Farewell for now."
    Z "Fue perspicaz hablar contigo. Adiós por ahora."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3265
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_767d17c9:

    # Stm "Farewell, friend. May our paths cross again."
    Stm "Adiós, amigo. Que nuestros caminos vuelvan a cruzarse."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3278
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_d8d540ee:

    # "You spot [I] sitting on the roof, and decide to join her..."
    "Ves a [I] sentada en el techo, y decides unirte a ella..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3281
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3282
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_020709bf:

    # Z "How's the drink?"
    Z "¿Qué tal la bebida?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3285
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3288
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_be10f844:

    # "You look at her. Last night has barely left a mark on her. You recognized it before, after you freed her from the decayed..."
    "La miras a ella. La noche pasada apenas ha dejado una marca en ella. Lo reconociste antes, después de liberarla de los descompuestos..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3290
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_3d352053:

    # Z "I have talked to the others. Things are indeed more complicated than they appeared to me."
    Z "He hablado con los demás. Las cosas son, de hecho, más complicadas de lo que me parecían."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3293
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_5018f220_2:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3294
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_cc60ca75:

    # "She looks aside..."
    "Ella mira hacia otro lado..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3297
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_34a49402:

    # I "We inherited cruel curses from our ancestors..."
    I "Heredamos crueles maldiciones de nuestros ancestros..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3300
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_9f729b2e:

    # Z "At least she's not going to be alone."
    Z "Al menos no va a estar sola."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3303
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_5018f220_3:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3304
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_84cfcbc3:

    # "You look at her, wondering if conditions like those of [I] and Chili were ever present or accepted before the world fell."
    "La miras, preguntándote si condiciones como las de [I] y Chili alguna vez fueron aceptadas antes de la caída del mundo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3305
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_63ab3238:

    # Z "In my years of wandering the desert and exploring the most unusual and sometimes extraordinary things and people..."
    Z "En mis años de vagar por el desierto y explorar las cosas y personas más inusuales y, a veces, extraordinarias..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3306
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_5018f220_4:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3307
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_8118a0e3:

    # Z "...I can see a connection of sorts between you and this tribe. Your lives seem to exist at the opposite sides of the swing of a pendulum."
    Z "... puedo ver una especie de conexión entre tú y esta tribu. Sus vidas parecen existir en los lados opuestos del balanceo de un péndulo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3310
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_151cf12c:

    # Z "But I can't help but wonder if this is a quirk of fate... a coincidence... a design..."
    Z "Pero no puedo evitar preguntarme si esto es una peculiaridad del destino... una coincidencia... un diseño..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3314
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_40067b8a:

    # "[I] considers your remarks for a while, in silence, considering whether to reply, and deciding against it."
    "[I] reflexiona sobre tus comentarios en silencio un momento, considerando si responder, y al final decide no hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3318
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_ac5a4559:

    # I "Will you... visit my place again soon?"
    I "¿Volverás... pronto a visitar mi casa?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3321
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_f20cacf3:

    # "She looks at you, expectantly..."
    "Ella te mira, expectante..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3322
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_3e74f63d:

    # Z "I shall... in time."
    Z "Lo haré... con el tiempo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3325
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_5018f220_5:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3328
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_3341037d:

    # "You leave [I] to her thoughts, and climb down the stairs..."
    "Dejas a [I] con sus pensamientos y bajas las escaleras..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3334
translate spanish d17a_tribesman_move_on_35bf15cf:

    # "You rest until you see members of the team gathering near the center..."
    "Descansas hasta que ves a miembros del equipo reuniéndose cerca del centro..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3340
translate spanish d17a627_ee99f685:

    # Fa "Hey, Red. Want to join us?"
    Fa "Ey, Red. ¿Quieres unirte a nosotros?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3341
translate spanish d17a627_2f47a8a5:

    # Fa "We could use your input."
    Fa "Podríamos necesitar tu aporte."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3344
translate spanish d17a627_445e41dd:

    # Re "Thanks, but..."
    Re "Gracias, pero..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3345
translate spanish d17a627_0c495a7f:

    # Re "...you guys got this."
    Re "... vosotros podéis con eso."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3348
translate spanish d17a627_bca4b7ac:

    # Re "I want to get this done before we leave."
    Re "Yo quiero terminar esto antes de que nos vayamos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3349
translate spanish d17a627_f1040380:

    # Re "Ah... damn it."
    Re "Ah... maldita sea."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3352
translate spanish d17a627_e7cbbf10:

    # Re "Can't wait for a proper bath, later. This dust is making me feel all sticky..."
    Re "No puedo esperar a darme un baño en condiciones más tarde. Este polvo me hace sentir pegajosa..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3355
translate spanish d17a627_810c7bdd:

    # Sc "Let's get this over with, then."
    Sc "Vamos a acabar con esto, entonces."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3358
translate spanish d17a627_03534a3e:

    # Sc "Okay. As far as I can see, there are two options on how to proceed."
    Sc "Vale. Hasta donde puedo ver, hay dos opciones sobre cómo proceder."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3359
translate spanish d17a627_1882e8fe:

    # Sc "Chili, your people either stick around in these ruins, waiting to be attacked again, or we ask them to join us."
    Sc "Chili, tu gente o se queda en estas ruinas, esperando ser atacados de nuevo, o les pedimos que se unan a nosotros."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3362
translate spanish d17a627_5d090823:

    # Sc "You wanted allies, Fangs? These people seem smart, and several of them could be willing to fight for something."
    Sc "¿Querías aliados, Fangs? Estas personas parecen inteligentes, y varios de ellos podrían estar dispuestos a luchar por algo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3365
translate spanish d17a627_f82635ce:

    # Chi "Excuse me, Scarp, but these are a bit more than ruins."
    Chi "Perdón, Scarp, pero esto es mucho más que unas ruinas."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3366
translate spanish d17a627_67d8d896:

    # Chi "Can I propose a different idea?"
    Chi "¿Puedo proponer una idea diferente?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3369
translate spanish d17a627_8982fb65:

    # Chi "This place... It could be fortified! Serve as an outpost for the people in the bunker."
    Chi "Este lugar... ¡Podría ser fortificado! ¡Servir como un puesto avanzado para la gente del búnker!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3370
translate spanish d17a627_2eaa99cb:

    # Chi "Sooner or later, you're going to be at full capacity. What will you do then? Start turning people away?"
    Chi "Tarde o temprano, estarás a plena capacidad. ¿Qué harás entonces? ¿Empezarás a rechazar gente?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3371
translate spanish d17a627_9440f439:

    # Fa "That won't be a problem for a long while. There are not that many of us around these parts. The occasional straggler brought in by Ivy barely counts."
    Fa "Eso no será un problema por mucho tiempo. No hay muchos de nosotros por aquí. Los pocos rezagados que Ivy trae casi no cuentan."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3372
translate spanish d17a627_ddb70019:

    # Sc "There's merit in having a second outpost or base, eventually."
    Sc "Hay mérito en tener un segundo puesto avanzado o base, eventualmente."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3375
translate spanish d17a627_21979be9:

    # Sc "But right now all it would do is stretch us too thin. We can't operate and defend the bunker {i}and{/i} this place at the same time."
    Sc "Pero ahora mismo, todo lo que haría sería estirarnos demasiado. No podemos operar y defender el búnker {i}y{/i} este lugar al mismo tiempo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3376
translate spanish d17a627_8b0efb22:

    # Sc "Fangs, what do you say?"
    Sc "Fangs, ¿qué dices?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3379
translate spanish d17a627_833f672e:

    # Fa "I... don't know. That's why I called you here, to discuss our next step."
    Fa "Yo... no sé. Por eso te llamé aquí, para discutir nuestro próximo paso."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3382
translate spanish d17a627_ddaa5818:

    # Chi "Then we should involve other members of the tribe."
    Chi "Entonces deberíamos involucrar a otros miembros de la tribu."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3385
translate spanish d17a627_6c4c5379:

    # Fa "You and Pepper are their best advocates. You have seen the bunker and know what we stand for."
    Fa "Tú y Pepper sois sus mejores defensores. Habéis visto el búnker y sabéis lo que representamos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3388
translate spanish d17a627_7868cfc9:

    # Pe "You already know what I think. Their best chance at survival is to join us."
    Pe "Ya sabes lo que pienso. Su mejor oportunidad de sobrevivir es unirse a nosotros."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3391
translate spanish d17a627_e0e97139:

    # Pe "There's too few of us to take on another attack by the next potential adversary."
    Pe "Somos muy pocos para enfrentar otro ataque del próximo adversario potencial."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3394
translate spanish d17a627_e1ae7b88:

    # Chi "We might have stepped out of it, but you can't ask the others that!"
    Chi "Podríamos haber salido de ahí, pero no puedes pedirle eso a los demás."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3397
translate spanish d17a627_9d0567d7:

    # Pe "What else can they do?"
    Pe "¿Qué más pueden hacer?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3398
translate spanish d17a627_d30a31b1:

    # Pe "We have joined the Bunker and its resources with good reason. If they could see the place..."
    Pe "Nos hemos unido al Búnker y sus recursos por una buena razón. Si pudieran ver el lugar..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3401
translate spanish d17a627_1bfa03d0:

    # Pe "They say we must look for answers. They say they still do, but have they made any progress?"
    Pe "Dicen que debemos buscar respuestas. Dicen que todavía lo hacen, pero ¿han hecho algún progreso?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3406
translate spanish d17a627_ac02ab2c:

    # Chi "So? Have you?"
    Chi "¿Y bien? ¿tú lo has hecho?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3409
translate spanish d17a627_2e3987c0:

    # Pe "..."
    Pe "..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3413
translate spanish d17a627_0e997b7b:

    # Pe "You know I am doing my best..."
    Pe "Sabes que estoy haciendo mi mejor esfuerzo..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3416
translate spanish d17a627_48612970:

    # Chi "I am sorry, sister, I... don't even want you to..."
    Chi "Lo siento, hermana, yo... ni siquiera quiero que tú..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3422
translate spanish d17a627_f99019f3:

    # "Another moment of silence follows, as every member of this small improvised council reflects on what they know about the tribe and about the two sisters in particular."
    "Otro momento de silencio sigue, mientras cada miembro de este pequeño consejo improvisado reflexiona sobre lo que saben de la tribu y de las dos hermanas en particular."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3423
translate spanish d17a627_4ae885c8:

    # Pe "I have not made much progress, no..."
    Pe "No he avanzado mucho, no..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3424
translate spanish d17a627_c009fa1e:

    # Pe "...but what if I had? You know the Sapa is all about the quest, and it is fundamentally tied to our mortality..."
    Pe "... pero, ¿y si lo hubiera hecho? Sabes que el Sapa trata de la búsqueda, y está fundamentalmente ligado a nuestra mortalidad..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3425
translate spanish d17a627_12dd36e8:

    # Sc "Well, that's just fucking dumb."
    Sc "Bueno, eso es simplemente estúpido."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3427
translate spanish d17a627_cb61f96c:

    # "Pepper's tone snaps into a sharp one..."
    "El tono de Pepper se vuelve agudo..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3428
translate spanish d17a627_4824df94:

    # Pe "Would you care to explain yourself? What do you know abou-..."
    Pe "¿Podrías explicarte? ¿Qué sabes sobre...?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3429
translate spanish d17a627_78f52c3e:

    # Sc "Oh, stop it will you? Woe is me, I'm so special because I have a timer that tells me when I will die."
    Sc "¡Oh, para ya, ¿quieres? Ay de mí, soy tan especial porque tengo un temporizador que me dice cuándo moriré."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3430
translate spanish d17a627_8a458628:

    # Sc "Do you think that we don't die? That we don't hold life as precious and worthy of celebrating? That we don't honour our dead?"
    Sc "¿Crees que nosotros no morimos? ¿Que nosotros no consideramos la vida como algo precioso y digno de celebrar? ¿Que nosotros no honramos a nuestros muertos?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3431
translate spanish d17a627_db4a62e7:

    # Sc "If anything, not knowing when it will end makes it just as important to us."
    Sc "Si acaso, no saber cuándo terminará lo hace igual de importante para nosotros."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3433
translate spanish d17a627_095930fe:

    # "No one seems to want to pick up on her words for some moments..."
    "Nadie parece querer retomar sus palabras por unos momentos..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3436
translate spanish d17a627_1848b28d:

    # Fa "We must go back to consider the situation practically."
    Fa "Debemos volver a considerar la situación de forma práctica."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3439
translate spanish d17a627_661353cf:

    # Z "Then let's be practical. Chili mentioned that the tribe used to travel, or have travelled and moved the tribe around before."
    Z "Entonces, seamos prácticos. Chili mencionó que la tribu solía viajar, o ha viajado y movido la tribu antes."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3440
translate spanish d17a627_4de7fae1:

    # Z "These people are smart. We could help bolster their defenses. In return, what can they offer? Their crops?"
    Z "Estas personas son inteligentes. Podríamos ayudar a reforzar sus defensas. A cambio, ¿qué pueden ofrecer? ¿Sus cultivos?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3443
translate spanish d17a627_4d202b03:

    # Sc "Right? Crops are one thing. Fangs, you know what we really need is one thing: Manpower."
    Sc "¿Cierto? Los cultivos son una cosa. Fangs, sabes que lo que realmente necesitamos es una cosa: Mano de obra."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3444
translate spanish d17a627_2d958dae:

    # Sc "Let them join our ranks. For people who talk and think about dying so much, we can give them a purpose to die for."
    Sc "Dejemos que se unan a nuestras filas. Para la gente que habla y piensa tanto sobre morir, podemos darles un propósito por el cual morir."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3447
translate spanish d17a627_101ffb22:

    # Chi "I-I don't know, but... is it worth throwing away hundreds of years of our tradition? Many here aren't fighters..."
    Chi "N-no lo sé, pero... ¿vale la pena tirar por la borda cientos de años de nuestra tradición? Muchos aquí no son luchadores..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3450
translate spanish d17a627_c604a175:

    # Sc "Doing your part for the common good doesn't necessarily mean taking up arms. There are other ways to fight."
    Sc "Cumplir con tu parte por el bien común no necesariamente significa tomar las armas. Hay otras formas de luchar."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3451
translate spanish d17a627_341b8bb7:

    # Sc "Hells, you have kept our machines running. That alone has given us an edge."
    Sc "Gracias a ti nuestras máquinas siguen funcionando. Eso solo ya nos ha dado una ventaja."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3454
translate spanish d17a627_01adbbda:

    # Chi "I know that... but there are other ways they could contribute, without giving up on the journey!"
    Chi "Lo sé... pero hay otras formas en las que podrían contribuir, ¡sin renunciar al viaje!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3457
translate spanish d17a627_767d85c4:

    # Chi "We're not out here only being attacked by tribes trying to conquer!"
    Chi "¡No estamos aquí fuera siendo atacados solo por tribus que intentan conquistar!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3458
translate spanish d17a627_ddec7d59:

    # Chi "If you hide in a bunker, you will no longer encounter all the people that come through here!"
    Chi "¡Si te escondes en un búnker, ya no te cruzarás con todas las personas que pasan por aquí!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3461
translate spanish d17a627_f54d39c4:

    # Chi "There were many travellers over the years... traders, and even lonely people looking for a place to stay. Some even joined the tribe!"
    Chi "Hubo muchos viajeros a lo largo de los años... comerciantes e incluso personas solitarias buscando un lugar donde quedarse. ¡Algunos incluso se unieron a la tribu!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3464
translate spanish d17a627_2dafcf59:

    # Chi "We could set this place up to invite more people to the bunker. Many more than Ivy could ever reach out to!"
    Chi "Podríamos acondicionar este lugar para invitar a más gente al búnker. ¡Muchas más de las que Ivy podría alcanzar jamás!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3467
translate spanish d17a627_26f5597e:

    # Pe "{i}*sigh*{/i} Mina..."
    Pe "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Mina..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3470
translate spanish d17a627_5974bdf4:

    # Pe "...look at this place. Look at the people... what is there left to live for here?"
    Pe "... mira este lugar. Mira a la gente... ¿qué queda para vivir aquí?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3471
translate spanish d17a627_9d5396b1:

    # Chi "What? We grew up here! Our family lived here for a long time. You know our parents never needed much either!"
    Chi "¿Qué? ¡Nos criamos aquí! ¡Nuestra familia vivió aquí durante mucho tiempo! ¡Sabes que nuestros padres tampoco necesitaban mucho!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3472
translate spanish d17a627_74fedb5e:

    # Chi "I think you would change these people at the core. Many do not believe in conflict..."
    Chi "Creo que cambiarías a estas personas desde la raíz. Muchos no creen en el conflicto..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3473
translate spanish d17a627_414c416f:

    # Chi "The Sapa is about accepting our lives, no matter how short. I grew up living each day as it is our last."
    Chi "El Sapa consiste en aceptar nuestras vidas, sin importar lo cortas que sean. Crecí viviendo cada día como si fuera el último."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3474
translate spanish d17a627_efbe1852:

    # Chi "The bunker... is just not that... I'm sorry..."
    Chi "El búnker... no es... lo siento..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3475
translate spanish d17a627_1f5407dc:

    # Fa "It is not... It's a means to an end. We want better lives for ourselves. Once we achieve that, we can leave the bunker behind."
    Fa "No es... Es un medio para un fin. Queremos mejores vidas para nosotros mismos. Una vez que logremos eso, podemos dejar el búnker atrás."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3478
translate spanish d17a627_1c192da8:

    # Sc "I think we all have made our points. Let's cast our votes. I'm for taking them in."
    Sc "Creo que todos hemos dado nuestros puntos. Votemos. Yo estoy a favor de aceptarlos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3481
translate spanish d17a627_f716866d:

    # Pe "Assimilation it is, for me. Sorry, sister."
    Pe "Para mí, es la asimilación. Lo siento, hermana."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3484
translate spanish d17a627_6cbf1e54:

    # Chi "It's okay. Whatever happens, we make a choice together..."
    Chi "Está bien. Pase lo que pase, tomaremos la decisión juntos..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3487
translate spanish d17a627_89013665:

    # Chi "I would vote for defending this place, and repairing the time-piece!"
    Chi "¡Yo votaría por defender este lugar y reparar el reloj del tiempo!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3490
translate spanish d17a627_3982210d:

    # Sc "Fangs?"
    Sc "¿Fangs?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3493
translate spanish d17a627_a545865e:

    # Fa "I... You guys do the voting, this time."
    Fa "Yo... Esta vez votad vosotros."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3498
translate spanish d17a627_38a4e77f:

    # Sc "[persistent.player_name]? What's your vote?"
    Sc "[persistent.player_name] ¿Cuál es tu voto?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3504
translate spanish d17a627_b688d553:

    # Z "I vote to let the people here move into the bunker."
    Z "Voto para permitir que las personas aquí se muden al búnker."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3508
translate spanish d17a627_6ec2b410:

    # Z "I vote to guard this place. Let the people here support the bunker in their own way."
    Z "Voto por proteger este lugar. Que las personas aquí apoyen al búnker a su manera."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3512
translate spanish d17a627_660a2803:

    # Sc "Krait? What do you think?"
    Sc "¿Krait? ¿Qué piensas?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3515
translate spanish d17a627_6a66bd28:

    # Kr "..."
    Kr "..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3518
translate spanish d17a627_5d6c097d:

    # Kr "I think that there are still a few nice things out there. The view is pretty here."
    Kr "Creo que todavía hay algunas cosas bonitas ahí fuera. La vista aquí es preciosa."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3521
translate spanish d17a627_0f24a20f:

    # Kr "Look at it. You've travelled the desert, you've seen those mountains. Do you think they care about our petty squabbles?"
    Kr "Míralo. Has viajado por el desierto, has visto esas montañas. ¿Crees que les importan nuestras pequeñas disputas?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3523
translate spanish d17a627_43772319:

    # Sc "..."
    Sc "..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3527
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_fa42d186:

    # Kr "Do whatever you want."
    Kr "Haz lo que quieras."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3531
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_bb0cd7fa:

    # Sc "Fine... I think that concludes it, then."
    Sc "Vale... creo que eso lo concluye."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3537
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_ffae5293:

    # Sc "That's three to one. So we agree to renew our proposal to join us."
    Sc "Eso es tres contra uno. Entonces acordamos renovar nuestra propuesta para unirnos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3538
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_7965d66f:

    # Fa "Let's go talk to them... and see what they will say about it."
    Fa "Vamos a hablar con ellos... y veamos qué dicen al respecto."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3540
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_a0e95b53:

    # Fa "Once we have their answer, we'll know what to do. {w=3} {nw}"
    Fa "Una vez que tengamos su respuesta, sabremos qué hacer.{w=3} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3544
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_bea058ca:

    # Chi "Then life might change for everyone here. {w=3} {nw}"
    Chi "Entonces la vida podría cambiar para todos aquí. {w=3} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3547
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_5af63f90:

    # Pe "Just as it did for us, Mina, for the better. {w=3} {nw}"
    Pe "Así como fue para nosotras, Mina, para mejor. {w=3} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3550
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_854f2d9b:

    # Pe "You will see. There is no need to worry. {w=2.5} {nw}"
    Pe "Ya lo verás. No hay necesidad de preocuparse. {w=2.5} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3555
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_d4074ba8:

    # "She moves away... {w=1.5} {nw}"
    "Ella se aleja... {w=1.5} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3558
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_f75362f8:

    # Pe "We might leave this place for good, yes... {w=3.5} {nw}"
    Pe "Podríamos abandonar este lugar para siempre, sí... {w=3.5} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3559
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_c51ecc58:

    # Pe "...but that doesn't mean they have to abandon everything. I might have an idea... {w=4.5} {nw}"
    Pe "... pero eso no significa que tengan que abandonar todo. Puede que tenga una idea... {w=4.5} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3569
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_7a02ef4a:

    # Sc "That's two in favour, two against... Chili and [persistent.player_name]'s voice against mine and Pepper's."
    Sc "Dos a favor, dos en contra... La voz de Chili y [persistent.player_name] contra la mía y la de Pepper."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3570
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_13bd14c4:

    # Sc "Fangs... you're the leader for a reason. You need to break the tie here."
    Sc "Fangs... eres la líder por una razón. Tú tienes que romper el empate."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3571
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_cb8cbf59:

    # Fa "..."
    Fa "..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3572
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_92046222:

    # Fa "I suppose we could lend these people a hand."
    Fa "Supongo que podríamos echar una mano a estas personas."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3573
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_a5940d23:

    # Pe "...?"
    Pe "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3575
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_00797fad:

    # Fa "My vote is for Chili. Let's ask them if they want our protection."
    Fa "Mi voto es para Chili. Preguntémosles si quieren nuestra protección."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3577
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_3ff5d87e:

    # Sc "Hm... fine."
    Sc "Hm... está bien."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3580
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_20fa4ff5:

    # Sc "I will ask their leaders what they think of it. {w=3.5} {nw}"
    Sc "Les preguntaré a sus líderes qué piensan al respecto. {w=3.5} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3583
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_b95859ba:

    # Chi "And I will get to work as well! {w=3} {nw}"
    Chi "¡Y yo también me pondré a trabajar! {w=3} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3589
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_f850f1f5:

    # "She quickly gets up... {w=3} {nw}"
    "Ella se levanta rápidamente... {w=3} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3593
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_1b78a30f:

    # Pe "Mina... {w=2} {nw}"
    Pe "Mina... {w=2} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3596
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_d8801b3f:

    # Chi "Hmm... where do I start? {w=2.7} {nw}"
    Chi "Hmm... ¿por dónde empiezo? {w=2.7}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3599
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_5a3a242f:

    # Chi "First, I will make sure to get you running again. {w=2.3} {nw}"
    Chi "Primero, me aseguraré de que vuelvas a funcionar. {w=2.3}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3600
translate spanish d17a_ending_cutscenes_7b3bdc42:

    # Chi "I would say it's about time! {w=2} {nw}"
    Chi "Diría que ya era hora. {w=2} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3611
translate spanish d17b_c98c889f:

    # C "[persistent.player_name]... wake up..."
    C "[persistent.player_name]... despierta..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3614
translate spanish d17b_ac943dc1:

    # Z "Mh... Fangs?"
    Z "Mh... ¿Fangs?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3617
translate spanish d17b_8b75023c:

    # Fa "Sorry for interrupting your sleep. There is someone who wanted to see you."
    Fa "Perdón por interrumpir tu sueño. Alguien quería verte."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3620
translate spanish d17b_033c5023:

    # Z "Someone... okay, who is it."
    Z "Alguien... de acuerdo, ¿quién es?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3623
translate spanish d17b_dcbc7c5c:

    # C "Hey..."
    C "Ey..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3626
translate spanish d17b_6a69ace7:

    # C "Do you...remember me?"
    C "¿Tú... me recuerdas?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3629
translate spanish d17b_2b58f029:

    # "The girl speaks with a lisp, as she stands near the edge of the bed, with a tremor betraying her anxiety..."
    "La chica habla con un leve ceceo mientras está cerca del borde de la cama, con un temblor que delata su ansiedad..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3630
translate spanish d17b_5c62d38a:

    # Z "Remind me again?"
    Z "¿Me lo recuerdas?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3633
translate spanish d17b_0cc833a9:

    # C "Oh... maybe you can't see me."
    C "¡Oh... tal vez no puedas verme!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3636
translate spanish d17b_ece38162:

    # "She gets closer, in a few short steps."
    "Se acerca, en unos pocos pasos cortos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3639
translate spanish d17b_19d1f2a9:

    # C "Maybe now!"
    C "¿Quizás ahora?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3642
translate spanish d17b_2d0215b6:

    # C "I am Slink. Several weeks ago, you saved me from this big brute in the market!"
    C "Soy Slink. Hace unas semanas, me salvaste de ese bruto enorme en el mercado."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3645
translate spanish d17b_0749055d:

    # Z "Ah... I remember that. I didn't get a good look at you then."
    Z "Ah... Recuerdo eso. No te vi bien en ese entonces."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3646
translate spanish d17b_1c17006a:

    # "Her frame is small and lithe, and as you look her in the eyes, you have a notion that she must have lived a hard life, and seen much adversity."
    "Su figura es pequeña y ágil, y al mirarla a los ojos, tienes la noción de que debe haber llevado una vida difícil y visto mucha adversidad."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3649
translate spanish d17b_ab5ae34a:

    # Fa "Our new girl here had been sneaking into the city and stealing from its good people at night..."
    Fa "Nuestra nueva chica aquí había estado colándose en la ciudad y robando a las buenas personas por la noche..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3650
translate spanish d17b_d4e479e9:

    # Fa "She was lucky that Ivy found her before she got herself into real trouble..."
    Fa "Tuvo suerte de que Ivy la encontrara antes de que se metiera en un verdadero problema..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3651
translate spanish d17b_1a410ea6:

    # Fa "...isn't that right, Slink?"
    Fa "... ¿no es así, Slink?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3654
translate spanish d17b_887f4613:

    # Sli "Oh... about that..."
    Sli "¡Oh... sobre eso...!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3657
translate spanish d17b_4fd32df3:

    # Fa "Come on, you wanted to show the man how thankful you are."
    Fa "Vamos, querías mostrarle al hombre lo agradecida que estás."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3660
translate spanish d17b_d744b46c:

    # Sli "Yes... I do."
    Sli "Sí... lo hago."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3663
translate spanish d17b_59ee0905:

    # Sli "{i}*kiss*{/i}"
    Sli "{i}*besando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3666
translate spanish d17b_bf08ef6f:

    # Sliw "Thank you, sir, for saving my life."
    Sliw "Gracias, señor, por salvarme la vida."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3669
translate spanish d17b_b1d744b9:

    # Z "That was not..."
    Z "Eso no fue..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3672
translate spanish d17b_3113ab32:

    # Fa "Weren't you trying to learn to restrain yourself?"
    Fa "¿No estabas tratando de aprender a controlarte?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3675
translate spanish d17b_d3f8c502:

    # Z "Restrain myself?"
    Z "¿Controlarme?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3678
translate spanish d17b_80ea09be:

    # Fa "Not you, her, Slink! She knows she can get too.. physical."
    Fa "Tú no, ella, ¡Slink! Sabe que puede ser demasiado... física."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3679
translate spanish d17b_5128d8ad:

    # Fa "Here, I'll show you something."
    Fa "Aquí, te voy a mostrar algo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3682
translate spanish d17b_c9c4862f:

    # "Fangs pulls the girl close and wraps her arm around her..."
    "Fangs levanta a la chica y pasa su brazo por su hombro..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3685
translate spanish d17b_32f0129b:

    # Fa "You probably didn't notice but as it turns out, you and Ivy found me a..."
    Fa "Probablemente no lo notaste, pero como resultó, tú e Ivy me encontrasteis una..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3686
translate spanish d17b_0c7d4dc9:

    # Fa "...little sister of sorts."
    Fa "... pequeña hermana, en cierto sentido."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3689
translate spanish d17b_bcf86a55:

    # Fa "Come on, show him what I mean."
    Fa "Vamos, enséñale lo que quiero decir."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3692
translate spanish d17b_73e9d150:

    # Sli "Ah..."
    Sli "Ah..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3693
translate spanish d17b_ed7e8ccf:

    # Fa "Good girl."
    Fa "Buena chica."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3696
translate spanish d17b_b1f49d10:

    # Fa "Our little wasteland devil is not as innocent as she seems."
    Fa "Nuestra diablilla del páramo no es tan inocente como parece."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3697
translate spanish d17b_3712d6dc:

    # Fa "That man you confronted wasn't her first...prey."
    Fa "El hombre que confrontaste no fue su primera... presa."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3700
translate spanish d17b_7b7f9423:

    # Sli "Ha..."
    Sli "Ha..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3701
translate spanish d17b_edb9a3bd:

    # Fa "But... now that she is under my... supervision, she might just learn to behave."
    Fa "Pero... ahora que está bajo mi... supervisión, quizá aprenda a comportarse."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3704
translate spanish d17b_9bf4c0e2:

    # Fa "Na-ah... don't you dare bite me again..."
    Fa "¡Na-ah... ni se te ocurra morderme otra vez...!"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3707
translate spanish d17b_08620639:

    # Sli "Mh..."
    Sli "Mh..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3708
translate spanish d17b_1bb8a400:

    # Fa "That's better..."
    Fa "Eso está mejor..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3711
translate spanish d17b_d51f9ea8:

    # Sli "Mhm..."
    Sli "Mhm..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3712
translate spanish d17b_8aac8459:

    # Fa "There... all you need to do is listen to me."
    Fa "Ahí... todo lo que necesitas hacer es escucharme."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3715
translate spanish d17b_56e980f9:

    # Fa "Thank you for bringing her to me. I will continue to personally train her."
    Fa "Gracias por traerla a mí. Continuaré entrenándola personalmente."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3718
translate spanish d17b_7f923d98:

    # Z "Yeah... you girls have fun training tonight."
    Z "Sí... diviértanse entrenando esta noche."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3719
translate spanish d17b_2e49191a:

    # Z "Let me know whenever you need my advice. I'll go back to sleep."
    Z "Házmelo saber siempre que necesites mi consejo. Volveré a dormir."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3722
translate spanish d17b_7b77f27b:

    # Fa "Have a good rest."
    Fa "Descansa bien."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3727
translate spanish d17b_0bfdcc5b:

    # "As they leave, you go back to sleep..."
    "Cuando se van, vuelves a dormirte..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3740
translate spanish d17c_2bb75417:

    # Pe "Hello, [persistent.player_name]."
    Pe "Hola, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3741
translate spanish d17c_91b38510:

    # Z "Pepper..."
    Z "Pepper..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3744
translate spanish d17c_d73f0014:

    # Pe "Good that you're here. If you have a moment, I have something I want to say to you."
    Pe "Qué bueno que estés aquí. Si tienes un momento, tengo algo que quiero decirte."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3747
translate spanish d17c_849be25d:

    # Z "I'm listening..."
    Z "Estoy escuchando..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3750
translate spanish d17c_54b5f545:

    # "She walks by you, puts her notebook down and leans against the machine..."
    "Pasa junto a ti, deja su cuaderno y se apoya en la máquina..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3753
translate spanish d17c_f366b6bd:

    # Pe "Thank you for fighting with us."
    Pe "Gracias por luchar con nosotros."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3756
translate spanish d17c_7f15aecf:

    # Pe "Specifically, thank you for protecting my sister."
    Pe "Especialmente, gracias por proteger a mi hermana."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3759
translate spanish d17c_0ef9e576:

    # Z "You're welcome. Also... I came to ask you, just so I know..."
    Z "De nada. También... vine a preguntarte, solo por saber..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3760
translate spanish d17c_8fc1b4b6:

    # Z "What is your number?"
    Z "¿Cuál es tu número?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3763
translate spanish d17c_c3f399f4:

    # Pe "You don't have to worry about me, [persistent.player_name]. My number is forty two."
    Pe "No tienes que preocuparte por mí, [persistent.player_name]. Mi número es cuarenta y dos."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3766
translate spanish d17c_841b7fc9:

    # Pe "I still have fifteen years. The real urgency on my research comes from my sister, who has less than half of that."
    Pe "Aún me quedan quince años. La verdadera urgencia de mi investigación viene de mi hermana, que tiene menos de la mitad."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3769
translate spanish d17c_54440acf:

    # Pe "As you know, Mina is the main reason why I joined Fangs' group, and why I am working here."
    Pe "Como sabes, Mina es la razón principal por la que me uní al grupo de Fangs y por la que trabajo aquí."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3772
translate spanish d17c_067c2a76:

    # Pe "I just don't want to lose her. I didn't leave my tribe to come here, only to see her die in some random fight."
    Pe "Simplemente no quiero perderla. No dejé mi tribu para venir aquí solo para verla morir en una pelea cualquiera."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3774
translate spanish d17c_1d850671:

    # Pe "That said, now that my former tribe has opened the door to this place, I am highly motivated to continue."
    Pe "Eso dicho, ahora que mi antigua tribu ha abierto la puerta a este lugar, estoy muy motivado para continuar."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3776
translate spanish d17c_c19354e7:

    # Pe "Either way, I am going back to my work, especially now that I don't have to hide my true purpose from Fangs anymore."
    Pe "De cualquier manera, vuelvo a mi trabajo, especialmente ahora que ya no tengo que ocultar mi verdadero propósito a Fangs."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3779
translate spanish d17c_e933bb36:

    # Pe "The research to figure out the difference in the genome between my people and men of... your kind, demands more work..."
    Pe "El trabajo para averiguar la diferencia en el genoma entre mi gente y los hombres de... tu tipo, necesita más investigación..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3783
translate spanish d17c_bea49e61:

    # Pe "...and yes, that includes you, too."
    Pe "... y sí, eso también te incluye a ti."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3787
translate spanish d17c_49fd4f67:

    # Pe "Regardless... I have said my piece. You have my appreciation."
    Pe "De todos modos... he dicho lo que tenía que decir. Tienes mi agradecimiento."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3788
translate spanish d17c_b6ebd3d6:

    # Pe "Now... if you'll excuse me... I have to get back to work."
    Pe "Ahora... si me disculpas... tengo que volver al trabajo."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3791
translate spanish d17c_d53567d2:

    # Z "Very well. See you around then, Pepper."
    Z "Muy bien. Nos vemos luego, Pepper."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3794
translate spanish d17c_579a1e2c:

    # "You leave the laboratory..."
    "Abandonas el laboratorio..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3798
translate spanish d17c_193e1a8d:

    # Pe "So, are you willing to continue donating samples?"
    Pe "¿Estás dispuesto a seguir donando muestras?"

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3807
translate spanish d17c8_d3621a48:

    # Z "I am ready whenever you need me."
    Z "Estoy listo siempre que me necesites."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3810
translate spanish d17c8_6819a952:

    # Pe "I hoped so."
    Pe "Eso esperaba."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3813
translate spanish d17c8_71546f22:

    # Pe "However, I have maintenance and cleaning work to do today."
    Pe "Sin embargo, hoy tengo trabajo de mantenimiento y limpieza que hacer."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3816
translate spanish d17c8_56d8d66c:

    # Pe "From tomorrow onward, you may visit me so I can continue helping you donate samples."
    Pe "A partir de mañana, puedes visitarme para que pueda seguir ayudándote a donar muestras."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3821
translate spanish d17c8_785268b4:

    # Z "That depends. It's getting repetitive, Pepper."
    Z "Eso depende. Se está volviendo repetitivo, Pepper."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3822
translate spanish d17c8_e4f095e4:

    # Z "Don't take it as an insult to your... manual skills."
    Z "No lo tomes como un insulto a tus... habilidades manuales."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3825
translate spanish d17c8_fc03d074:

    # Pe "I see where you are coming from, and I won't."
    Pe "Veo de dónde vienes, y no lo haré."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3828
translate spanish d17c8_430311b0:

    # Pe "However, I don't need to remind you that we are not a couple, and that my way to helping you climax is exclusively for scientific reasons."
    Pe "Sin embargo, no necesito recordarte que no somos pareja y que mi forma de ayudarte a llegar al clímax es exclusivamente por razones científicas."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3831
translate spanish d17c8_6ff8d332:

    # Pe "If you have suggestions on how to speed up the procedure, you may make them next time. But I will not promise anything."
    Pe "Si tienes sugerencias sobre cómo acelerar el procedimiento, puedes hacerlas la próxima vez. Pero no prometo nada."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3835
translate spanish d17c8_5ae6fe3e:

    # Z "Very well..."
    Z "Muy bien..."

# game/scripts/day17.rpy:3838
translate spanish d17c8_579a1e2c:

    # "You leave the laboratory..."
    "Abandonas el laboratorio..."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:218
    old "Get to the point"
    new "Ve al grano."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:218
    old "Look at her"
    new "Mírala."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:271
    old "\"I didn't know the bunker has other outside connections.\""
    new "\"No sabía que el búnker tenía otras conexiones externas.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:271
    old "\"You are too educated to come from some tribe.\""
    new "\"Estás demasiado educada para venir de una tribu.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:271
    old "\"So what do you need me for?\""
    new "\"¿Entonces para qué me necesitas?\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:400
    old "\"You like it loud!\""
    new "\"¡Te gusta que sea ruidoso!\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:400
    old "\"What is this noise?!\""
    new "\"¡¿Qué es este ruido?!\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:473
    old "\"I don't get it\""
    new "\"No lo entiendo.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:473
    old "\"They stored bows in here, and now hand cannons?\""
    new "\"¿Guardaban arcos aquí, y ahora cañones de mano?\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:700
    old "\"Let's start at the beginning. Tell me about Pepper.\""
    new "\"Empecemos desde el principio. Háblame de Pepper.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:700
    old "\"Tell me about Chili.\""
    new "\"Háblame de Chili.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:700
    old "\"What about Krait?\""
    new "\"¿Qué hay de Krait?\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:700
    old "\"Want to let off some steam?\""
    new "\"¿Quieres desahogarte un poco?\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:700
    old "\"No more questions. I'm ready to go.\""
    new "\"Sin más preguntas. Estoy listo para ir.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:819
    old "\"She definitely looks enticing.\""
    new "\"Definitivamente parece atractiva.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:819
    old "\"You're more my type.\""
    new "\"Tú eres más mi tipo.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:819
    old "\"I might pass.\""
    new "\"Podría pasar.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:840
    old "\"You're strong.\""
    new "\"Eres fuerte.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:840
    old "\"Your looks.\""
    new "\"Tu apariencia.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:840
    old "\"Your attitude.\""
    new "\"Tu actitud.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:872
    old "\"Because you are a challenge to defeat.\""
    new "\"Porque eres un desafío a vencer.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:872
    old "\"Because you stand up to me.\""
    new "\"Porque te enfrentas a mí.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:972
    old "\"They are normal people, mostly.\""
    new "\"Son personas normales, en su mayoría.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:972
    old "\"They are open minded in many ways.\""
    new "\"Son de mente abierta en muchos aspectos.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:972
    old "\"They are dutiful and tradionalist\""
    new "\"Son diligentes y tradicionalistas.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1170
    old "Check on [I]"
    new "Echar un vistazo a [I]."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1170
    old "Visit Red & Chili"
    new "Visita a Red y Chili."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1170
    old "Visit Krait"
    new "Visita a Krait."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1170
    old "Visit Scarp"
    new "Visita a Scarp."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1263
    old "\"I do like her. That's the reason.\""
    new "\"Me gusta. Esa es la razón.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1263
    old "\"Ivy led me to you.\""
    new "\"Ivy me llevó hasta vosotras.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1263
    old "\"Pepper needs my samples.\""
    new "\"Pepper necesita mis muestras.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1263
    old "\"I believe in your mission\""
    new "\"Creo en vuestra misión.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1263
    old "\"I like the adventure, and the gold...\""
    new "\"Me gusta la aventura, y el oro...\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1387
    old "\"One battle with you, a thousand more without you.\""
    new "\"Una batalla contigo, mil más sin ti.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1387
    old "\"So I don't care for your tone.\""
    new "\"Así que no me importa tu tono.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1421
    old "\"Good. I like a challenge.\""
    new "\"Bien. Me gustan los desafíos.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1421
    old "\"Words are not the only big things about me...\""
    new "\"Las palabras no son lo único grande de mí...\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:1421
    old "\"I have better things to do.\""
    new "\"Tengo cosas mejores que hacer.\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2687
    old "Caress her"
    new "Acaríciala."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2687
    old "Touch her shoulder"
    new "Tócale el hombro."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2687
    old "Move on"
    new "Prosigue"

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2841
    old "Why do you keep track of it?"
    new "¿Por qué lo llevas controlado?"

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2841
    old "You mentioned a journey. What's that about?"
    new "Mencionaste un viaje. ¿De qué trata eso?"

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2841
    old "What's the short pointer on the bottom right for?"
    new "¿Cuál es el marcador corto en la parte inferior derecha?"

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2841
    old "How does your condition work?"
    new "¿Cómo funciona tu condición?"

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2982
    old "Enter the building"
    new "Entrar en el edificio"

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2982
    old "See a tribesman"
    new "Echa un vistazo a un miembro de la tribu."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2982
    old "See [I]"
    new "Busca a [I]."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:2982
    old "Wait for the gathering"
    new "Espera a la reunión."

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:3012
    old "\"Do you grow your food in here?\""
    new "\"¿Cultiváis aquí vuestra comida?\""

    # game/scripts/day17.rpy:3012
